******
[2] Cholera - Cote d'Ivoire
Date: Mon 5 Jan 2015
Source: Burkina24 [in French, machine transl, edited]
http://burkina24.com/2015/01/05/cholera-plusieurs-dizaines-de-cas-et-des-deces-enregistres-en-cote-divoire/


While the Ivorian health authorities have been on alert to prevent the entry of Ebola on their territory, that country has been affected by a cholera epidemic with 139 proven cases and 9 deaths. The numbers continue to rise in the interior of the country and in Abidjan, particularly in the commune of Kumasi.

